  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"In this final moment, our hopes, fears and uncertainties come together in action.  We'd joke that there's no going back now, but that's really the point, isn't it?\"</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With those fateful words, you join the team of Hope Labs. A group of scientists & engineers, setting out to change the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Except, it all goes wrong. And now the team needs to band together, to fix the machine, to get back to normal, to before it all broke... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/41a8b0c3245a9d55918022813da58ea2.poster.avif?t=1752313546\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/41a8b0c3245a9d55918022813da58ea2.webm?t=1752313546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/41a8b0c3245a9d55918022813da58ea2.mp4?t=1752313546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Forgetful Loop is a worker-placement time puzzle game, where you and the team of 14 scientists/engineers are trying to fix a time-machine gone broken! Every second counts as the clock ticks to zero. But when it does, not all progress is lost! Can we fix the machine?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/3da4c2d5badae9f1563456a6dce98a53.avif?t=1752313546\" width=800 height=1247 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About <strong>6-8 Hours</strong> of content, with 7 main groups and 2 new groups with the 2025 update.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>59 Achievements</strong> to chase, with some tricky ones to challenge your skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls</strong>: Keyboard and Mouse controls, with rebinding support</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/b4c0b697381a6a3938efa6059d073580.avif?t=1752313546\" width=800 height=1300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Jennifer, Isabel, whatever's happening with you, I'm sorry -\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"- but we've only got seconds until we loop again.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"If you remember this conversation... help us fix the machine!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The loop restarts again.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"In this final moment, our hopes, fears and uncertainties come together in action.  We'd joke that there's no going back now, but that's really the point, isn't it?\"</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With those fateful words, you join the team of Hope Labs. A group of scientists & engineers, setting out to change the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Except, it all goes wrong. And now the team needs to band together, to fix the machine, to get back to normal, to before it all broke... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/41a8b0c3245a9d55918022813da58ea2.poster.avif?t=1752313546\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/41a8b0c3245a9d55918022813da58ea2.webm?t=1752313546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/41a8b0c3245a9d55918022813da58ea2.mp4?t=1752313546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Forgetful Loop is a worker-placement time puzzle game, where you and the team of 14 scientists/engineers are trying to fix a time-machine gone broken! Every second counts as the clock ticks to zero. But when it does, not all progress is lost! Can we fix the machine?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/3da4c2d5badae9f1563456a6dce98a53.avif?t=1752313546\" width=800 height=1247 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About <strong>6-8 Hours</strong> of content, with 7 main groups and 2 new groups with the 2025 update.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>59 Achievements</strong> to chase, with some tricky ones to challenge your skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls</strong>: Keyboard and Mouse controls, with rebinding support</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399540/extras/b4c0b697381a6a3938efa6059d073580.avif?t=1752313546\" width=800 height=1300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Jennifer, Isabel, whatever's happening with you, I'm sorry -\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"- but we've only got seconds until we loop again.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"If you remember this conversation... help us fix the machine!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The loop restarts again.</i></p>",
